improved_metadata.title: Spray Foam Cowboy
improved_metadata.description: This song is a humorous ode to the life of a spray foam insulation installer. It celebrates the work, the gear, and the feeling of accomplishment from sealing up a home.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: I'm gonna take my home Into your home, I'm gonna spray it till I can't no more
